column3:
* Davčna uprava Republike Slovenije je 1. oktobra 2011 uvedla nov informacijski sistem DURS, hkrati pa je bil uveden tudi spremenjen način vplačevanja javnofinančnih prihodkov. V obdobju od oktobra do decembra 2011 se, zaradi usklajevanja podatkov znotraj novega informacijskega sistema DURS v okviru vplačanih davčnih prihodkov, prihodkov iz naslova prispevkov za socialno varnost in drugih davkov, ne izkazuje realna realizacija, kar pa ne vpliva na skupno prikazano realizacijo prihodkov za to obdobje.
V korigirani realizaciji za oktober, november in december 2011 so posamezne kategorije davkov in prispevkov za socialno varnost ocenjene na podlagi dosežene dinamike posameznih kategorij v preteklih mesecih.
column4:
* On 1 October 2011, the Tax Administration of the Republic of Slovenia (DURS) introduced the new DURS information system to coincide with its modification of the fiscal revenue payment model. In the period from October till December 2011, owing to the need to coordinate data within the new information system, a large number of recorded data on the taxes and social security contributions paid to date do not reflect the actual results. However total revenues for this period are correct.
The adjusted realisation of tax receipts for October, November and December 2011 includes certain categories of taxes and social security contributions that were estimated on the basis of the level of certain categories of tax receipts in the past few months.
